EAGLE BOA
EAGLE BOA is an unspecified organization or group.<SEP>EAGLE BOA is an organization that holds a specific certification or status, as mentioned in the RFP requirements.

NAICS 561210
NAICS 561210 refers to the NAICS code for Marketing, Advertising, and Public Relations Services.<SEP>NAICS 561210 refers to the industry category for software publishers.

Section L

Section M

PWS Text
PWS text stands for Performance Work Statement, which outlines the requirements and expectations of a project or task.

Task Details
Task details refer to specific work items that need to be addressed in a proposal or project plan.

Capture Plan
The Capture Plan is a document that contains strategies and approaches for capturing business.

Shipley Proposal Guide
The Shipley Proposal Guide provides guidelines and best practices for writing proposals.

Proposal
A proposal is a formal document submitted to meet specific requirements or standards, as mentioned in the RFP.

Attachment A
Attachment A contains detailed task descriptions, PWS text, and other requirements as specified in the RFP.

EAGLE BOA holders
EAGLE BOA holders operate under NAICS 561210.
